## Project Context

- **Client:** Gerotech — Michigan CNC machinery distributor, Haas Factory Outlet, est. 1987
- **Agency:** CloudMellow (Matt)
- **This repo:** Static HTML/CSS/JS prototype (NOT the production build — final site will be WordPress)
- **Post-presentation next step:** Incorporate Rochelle's feedback, then proceed toward design phase

---

## Tech Stack

- Pure HTML5 / CSS3 (custom properties) / vanilla JS (ES6) — zero frameworks
- Font: Plus Jakarta Sans (400/500/600/700/800) via Google Fonts
- CSS load order: `assets/css/tokens.css` → `assets/css/components.css` → `assets/css/layout.css`
- JS: `nav.js` (both pages), `slider.js` (homepage only), `filter.js` (ES page only), `animations.js` (both)

## Key Brand Tokens
- Orange: `#F38A2C` (`--clr-orange`)
- Dark bg: `#1C1C21` (`--clr-dark-bg`)
- Dark nav/footer: `#3A3A40` (`--clr-dark-nav`)
- Max-width: 1200px (homepage) / 1120px (ES page)
- Radii: buttons 8px, cards 18–20px, pills 99px

---

## What NOT To Do

- Never replace `<div class="img-placeholder">` with real images until assets are confirmed
- Never guess at open client decisions — use placeholder + HTML comment
- Never use real FANUC logo — badge usage rights unconfirmed
- Never change CSS load order
- Never hardcode brand colors outside `tokens.css`
